---
title: Indian Spiced Sheperd's Pie with Garlicky Cabbage
description: Flavourful lamb mince mixed with sweet, tender root vegetables, topped with silky, smooth mashed potatoes and baked until golden and bubbling, the classic shepherd’s pie will never disappoint. We’ve added the fragrant kick of  Indian spice for a stand-out dish.
